e has been clicked on and viewed, excluding self-views. This metric is only visible to you.",viewsCountPopoverHeader:({count:e})=>`${e} views`},articlePreviewPage:{breadcrumbAriaLabel:"Breadcrumbs",commentAriaLabel:"Comment on this article",copyAriaLabel:"Copy URL",errorFetchingPreview:"Error fetching preview content",failedToLoadPreview:"Failed to load preview content",heroImageAlt:"Hero image",likeAriaLabel:"Like this article",loadingPreview:"Loading preview...",previewArticle:"Preview article"},bannedUserModal:{closeAriaLabel:"Close banned user modal",contactSupportLink:"contact support",header:"You cannot sign into Builder Center",message:"Your profile has been suspended for a violation of the AWS Builder Terms. If you think this is a mistake, contact support."},breadcrumbAriaLabel:"Breadcrumbs",cardActionReport:{archive:"Archive",cancel:"Cancel",closeModalAriaLabel:"Close modal",delete:"Delete",edit:"Edit",linkToComment:"Link to comment:",optionalLabel:"- optional",reasonLabel:"Reason for suspending",reasonPlaceholder:"Describe the reason for suspending",reportError:"An error occurred when trying to report this content.",reportQuestion:"What type of issue are you reporting?",reportSuccessMessage:"This content has been reported successfully. A moderator will review and take appropriate action.",selectReasonError:"Please select a reason for reporting this content.",shareAdditionalPlaceholder:"Any additional information?",shareAdditionalReport:"Do you have any additional information that will help us understand and handle the situation?",signInToReport:"Sign in to report content.",signInToSuspend:"Sign in to suspend this content.",suspendActionHeadline:"You are about to suspend this content",unsuspendAction:"Unsuspend",unsuspendActionHeadline:"You are about to unsuspend this content"},cardArticle:{copyButtonAriaLabel:"Copy Link",copyErrorText:"Link failed to copy",viewsCountAriaLabel:"Article views count",viewsCountPopoverBody:"Number of times your article has bee